859
01:02:33,835 --> 01:02:36,100
Ne!

860
01:02:36,200 --> 01:02:38,900
Ne, ne. Ne!

861
01:02:38,935 --> 01:02:41,600
Ne, Amanda! Ne!

862
01:03:11,800 --> 01:03:14,300
Hajde, Zoey. Hajde, van.

863
01:03:14,335 --> 01:03:16,300
Ne!

